Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:06.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, 2D-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:07.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:08.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you're lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.10,0:00:09.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:22.84,Dialogue5,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(296,306)}Ladies Talk
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:32.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aa yume no naka de aetara yueru ka na?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:57.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ne, kanashimi dake sora kara maiochite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:01:05.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sonna koe ga kimi o ima demo kurushimete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:09.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Soba de te o kasanetemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:13.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kono omoi wa kienai kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:21.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Futari me o awasetara hontou no koto yuenakutemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:25.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi no kotoba, dare yori mo sekai o terashiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:29.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tonari de kimi wa "Sayonara wa ai shiteru" tte, sou iu no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.65,0:01:31.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sunao ni narenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:33.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi dake kodoku o utattemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:35.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Egao ni narenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.22,0:01:37.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Arigato wa koi shiteru" tte sou iu no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ai no world's end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:57.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-san told me on the phone yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:00.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He said you've invited him to hang out several times,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:02.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but the timing's never right, and he felt bad turning you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you called me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:08.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I thought we could hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:12.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you busy with work, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:15.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:17.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have plans to see Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't call them plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:22.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She comes to my place almost every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:27.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So if you come over, the three of us can hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.78,0:02:30.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Should I call Yana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:35.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I tried calling him earlier, but he's busy again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:35.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:37.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:39.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't hung out in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:42.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could at least meet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:47.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I've been thinking... maybe he found a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:48.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You mean like a romantic relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:51.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:56.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's been turning down our invitations since summer vacation started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When I call him, he seems kind of flustered, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:02.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you're right, it must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:03.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Kouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:19.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It sounded like you were on the phone, so I tried to sneak in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:21.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who were you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:24.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,H-hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:28.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, 2D-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:29.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:30.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuo has a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Miss Ultrasonic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:36.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:38.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we should definitely find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:41.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:42.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:44.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:46.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to stalking Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:48.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:50.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:50.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:53.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Today's going to be a busy day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Miss Ultrasonic's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, I'm surprised you knew where this was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:05.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I got her address before summer break, so I could send her a summer greeting card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is Yana-san really going to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:11.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He will if he's seeing Miss Ultrasonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:12.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing Mitsuo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:16.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,he should be devoted enough to walk his girlfriend home after seeing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuo is busy today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:21.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Which means he has plans to go out with Miss Ultrasonic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Which means we'll catch him in the act if we wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:26.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My logic is flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:31.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But... isn't it too hot to be stalking someone today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already kinda bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go somewhere and get some shaved ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:41.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shaved ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:44.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:46.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't today a perfect day for shaved ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make you need to use the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:51.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:52.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:57.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get a good view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:02.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why is she carrying opera glasses around like it's normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:58.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Sneak, sneak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Sneak, sneak, sneak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:02.90,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(319,342)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Sneak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:05.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:06.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Eep!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:12.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to deliver your summer greeting card in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:14.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer break, so I thought\NI'd drop by to visit unannounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You should've called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:25.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm free today. I've been lazing around since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:26.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're free?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:29.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're not seeing anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:31.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:34.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm glad you came to hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:36.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:46.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:47.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A comedy routine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:52.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:57.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:01.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm living here, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:05.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:08.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We thought you were with Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:12.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Yana? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:17.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we thought Yana-san might have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:21.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We thought if he was dating someone, it'd be you, so we came to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:23.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:31.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen Yana since summer break started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not even once?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:40.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you made a big mistake, 2D-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:41.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:45.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who was so sure\NMitsuo would come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:49.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And you were the first one who said Mitsuo had a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you're here, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:04.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:06.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The moment you step over that threshold,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:09.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll officially recognize you as my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:12.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me before I step over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:21.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd known, I would've willed myself to stop, even if an explosive blast were blowing me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:24.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Kaga-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your shoes are so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:29.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you call me that name in that tone again,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:35.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll self-destruct, expel my brain from inside my exploded skull, and become an urban legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:36.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:39.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They're such idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:42.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My room's on the third floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:43.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You guys go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:58.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Does Miss Ultrasonic's family actually live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:05.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:06.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ultrasonic, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:09.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:13.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This place looks abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:17.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the process of moving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:18.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the last one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:24.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's moving back home because of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My mom decided to go with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, they left you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're originally from Fukuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't attend school from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:38.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, starting next month, I'll be living on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:43.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't found an apartment yet, and I'm kind of worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:45.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:49.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan... you've been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuoka's far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:09:00.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:01.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You get to live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:07.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to try living alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:10.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but now that I'm doing it, I'm full of anxiety and fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where you're going to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:14.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:20.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I need to find a place soon, and I want to save money, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:25.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to take the Okamera on a trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but this killed my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:31.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:33.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted to go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:39.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with Oka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:40.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it! All of us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:48.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ultrasonic, do you have a swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:50.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:53.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,M-my swimsuit should be around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:57.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make proper plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:58.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:01.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll invite Yana-san, and we'll all go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Summer only comes once a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:12.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:17.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get something to eat, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:20.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you where the film club gets food.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:26.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's a place that's cheap, but has good fried chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I go there with the film club all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:33.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but we didn't have to come so close to the university for it, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be one of our summer memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:40.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We might run into someone from the film club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:42.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There it is. It's already open...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:44.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}And their fried chicken is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:45.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:52.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That was Yana and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:54.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...Linda-senpai from the festival club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are those two doing together?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:01.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is Yana's girlfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:07.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Yana-san had unrequited feelings for Oka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go to the same place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:14.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:18.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they have some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:20.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave them alone for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:24.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with Miss Ultrasonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...quietly watch over Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:42.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um, why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:44.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm engaging in espionage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:47.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is how I dress for stealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I think it makes you stand out even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:56.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you'd better not tell anyone I came here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:57.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:58.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:03.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anyone to think you and I are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:05.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're so shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:06.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:10.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're here, let's try to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:11.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No! Way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:15.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:19.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:23.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you figure anything out about\NYana and Linda-senpai after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:28.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even seen them since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:31.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Is it bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:33.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:37.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this isn't the time for chit-chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:39.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We have an important mission today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:42.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:44.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:51.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,S-sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:55.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But, who shows up at someone's house and immediately strips?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:58.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I told you we'd be choosing swimsuits today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:01.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Think this'll charm Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:04.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You want to charm Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:06.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:09.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to use the perfect swimsuit to make him fall completely in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:13.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's already in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:15.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have nearly enough charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like he's not even half-charmed yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:20.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:21.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you have to take this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:30.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I brought all the swimsuits I had at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:31.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:35.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to change into a swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:38.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want us to match.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:41.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If we do, you'll have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this suddenly became a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Have you changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:46.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:47.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, and... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:53.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:55.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It looks weird, Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's too erotic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:01.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was going for a healthy look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sort of a Latin American island style...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:07.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no. We're in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A thong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can pull that off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:23.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you decided to show me before we went.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:27.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped you before you had an accident that would remain in everyone's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:30.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're having quite the accident yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:35.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:36.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:38.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:40.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a clay pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What were you thinking when you put that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:44.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:49.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like to dress too girly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:54.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This even looks like something you'd wear around the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:55.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dress girly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:15:00.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're dressing like a pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:05.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I think the designer was going for
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:08.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,a French enfant look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.67,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(281,354)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}enfant = child
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:11.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No. We're in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:12.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:13.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:16.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't think you have anything to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:22.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:25.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri's in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's plain as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:34.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like... Banri's afraid to try to get anything out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Have you not even kissed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:39.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:41.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:42.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:47.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not putting pressure on Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:52.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What does Banri have to do to satisfy you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:59.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to know I love him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:02.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying, "Get your freak on."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:06.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Follow your sexual desires and attack me like a wild beast."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:06.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Come on."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:07.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:10.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:13.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can say whatever you want if you use that voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:13.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:17.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In that case... put politely, you're saying, "Make love to me," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:24.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:29.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually pretty hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:31.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san, your boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:38.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:42.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I went to Banri's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:47.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,On the way home, the mood seemed right,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.87,0:16:50.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,so I went for a kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:51.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:57.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He seemed troubled and didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:00.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's like wrestling alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:05.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to smooth things over, but I'm a mess on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:09.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How were things going at his place before that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:13.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I made air yakisoba...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:14.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Air yakisoba?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:15.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:20.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I made Banri happy by cooking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:23.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We relaxed enveloped in the smell of yakisoba.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:29.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you never feel in the mood while spending hours in your boyfriend's apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:32.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:35.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:40.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I understand how Banri feels, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:42.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:44.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's just it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:46.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's that desperate face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you throw yourself at him like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:54.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,you'll make him feel like a demon accepting a sacrificial virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:18:02.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's hesitating because he wants to show that he really cares for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:08.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I know he cares about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:19.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But it's like Banri thinks of me as a doll or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:23.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're in quite a bind, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:29.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This year, I have plans to go to Barcelona on my annual family vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:31.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:41.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But, secretly... I want to create a situation that will let me stay in Tokyo with Banri, at his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:43.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:46.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The beach is a prelude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:49.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to know I'm serious about our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.82,0:18:50.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:55.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I always feel uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:58.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Does Banri really love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:02.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Will Banri suddenly disappear one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Banri, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:07.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:10.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is Banri still searching for himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What if he finds himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to leave me if he does?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:21.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:24.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about swimsuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about what's inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:26.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,About my feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:27.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,About fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:33.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wear the next one I grab.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll loan you the one I grab after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:36.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That'll settle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:37.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:39.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My swimsuit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:41.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And your swimsuit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:44.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:49.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have two school swimsuits?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:53.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That one's from middle school, and this one's from high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:57.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They're not bad, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:59.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This might actually be kind of interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:00.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:01.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:05.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This calls for the Okamera.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This can't possibly be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:14.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Some people will like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:18.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to charm Banri, not "people"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:23.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This might inspire a new fetish in Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:25.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:27.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:28.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:31.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kaga Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:37.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ultrasonic talked me into wearing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:39.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Oka Chinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you watching, Future Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:49.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm K-Kaga Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you watching, Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I love you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:56.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll love you today, tomorrow, and the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll love you forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:21:00.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the beach soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:04.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have fun and make memories that will last a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:12.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make that face!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:15.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You have two choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:16.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Choose whichever you prefer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:20.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is the innocent pair I bought in my third year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:26.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is the toxic pair the president gave me after the party the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:33.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think there was any chance\NI'd choose the toxic pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:39.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like you might actually wear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could've invited Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:47.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She said she's back home right now, so I didn't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:48.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:52.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where Linda-senpai's from.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:55.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:14.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Chigau yo mou, chigau tteba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:18.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aa, mada kizukanai no ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:24.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ni san jikan mo mae kara sono ude ni furetai noni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:27.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I do not need forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:30.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.61,0:22:38.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sakebitai kimochi wa hora komaru hodo aru noni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:44.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite doushite chittomo aa satotte kurenai no?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:51.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ne hontou ni hontou ni watashi ni koi shiteru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.67,0:22:57.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kosabayui kotoba wa iranai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.67,0:23:00.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Han eikyuuteki ni ai shite yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:03.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Gosen-nen go nado kyoumi wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:07.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Watashi endless de wa nai no
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.81,0:23:10.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuka wa shinu no yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:17.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Eien ni ai shiteru yo" nante yuwaretemo ureshikunai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.32,0:23:20.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mazu wa watashi o shinu made
